{"tid":707111,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句 街場南亞仔球品好過d街童同d濕鳩隊","createTime":"2018-06-18T12:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T12:35:37.000Z","uid":22407,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71d90041b5b6867ae4c772cdf11620f01cf92266","tid":707111,"uid":22407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"同過唔少球場南亞仔踢過波<br />\n佢地球品好過好多本地嘅球皇<br />\n至少唔會掂一掂就發晒脾氣 屌老母撩打交<br />\n又唔會矛鳩你 唔小心踢到省到你又會say sorry<br />\n唔似d街童或者嗰d濕鳩聯賽隊咁<br />\n下下都攞命唔收腳 <br />\n就嚟要簽生死狀先可以踢波<br />\n10場有5場都打交<br />\n唔係吹奏南亞仔 但係本地波牛真係幫唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34384cc5b8b6f13249d9d40b420217dc8d30208","tid":707111,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"你唔識打番佢地<br />\n<br />\n睇死你係D比人兇兩兇就SAY晒SORRY 然後走果D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f664c3b843c70a456272b31d0d463ac7f4e25a","tid":707111,"uid":184734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"有時有啲好撚上腳死扭爛扭埋去人堆，又間唔時反智轉身當自己球王，次次見到都好撚燥"},{"pid":"e50918ae9ddac881641203d75b53ac812a9fd424","tid":707111,"uid":22407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c34384cc5b8b6f13249d9d40b420217dc8d30208","tid":707111,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"你唔識打番佢地<br />\n<br />\n睇死你係D比人兇兩兇就SAY晒SORRY 然後走果D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"講緊球品 打返人就有球品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 成日俾人矛鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58db4d23be0bf58f81eef55ce7339e780effc9e5","tid":707111,"uid":22407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6